  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dab\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0d85\u0db0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0d9c\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db1 \u0daf\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d91\u0db4\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "If there is not enough fuel, do not speed the vehicle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Highway Maintenance Unit urges motorists using the highways to avoid entering the highway if they do not have enough fuel to drive to their destination.",
        "Digital boards have also been displayed stating that vehicles should not enter the Southern Expressway if there is not enough fuel."
      ],
